Shell icons — attribution and provenance
=========================================

Most icons in this directory (and the symbolic/ subdirectory) are derived from
Heroicons, the SOLID (filled) 24x24 set.

    Heroicons — MIT License
    https://github.com/tailwindlabs/heroicons
    Copyright (c) Tailwind Labs, Inc.

Heroicons is MIT licensed; redistribution and modification (including recolouring
via Slint `colorize:` / fill="currentColor") are permitted. The full MIT licence
text is available at the URL above.

All icons here use a 24x24 viewBox, fill="currentColor", and solid filled shapes
(no strokes), so the shell can tint them at runtime.


