CUSTOM icons — hand-authored in the Heroicons solid style
---------------------------------------------------------
(24x24 viewBox, fill="currentColor", evenodd, same optical weight as Heroicons.
 Heroicons has no 100%-matching metaphor for these.)

  symbolic/bluetooth.svg  CUSTOM — the Bluetooth rune (filled spine with the two
                                   triangular flags top and bottom).
  symbolic/contrast.svg   CUSTOM — dark/light split: a ring (Heroicons weight)
                                   with the right semicircle filled solid.
  symbolic/ethernet.svg   CUSTOM — an RJ45 / wired-network port (plug body, notch
                                   tab, three contact pins).
  symbolic/gauge.svg      CUSTOM — a speedometer/performance gauge (semicircular
                                   dial, needle, hub, tick marks).
  symbolic/wifi-off.svg   CUSTOM — the genuine Heroicons wifi glyph with a
                                   Heroicons-style diagonal slash (as bell-slash).
  bluetooth.svg           CUSTOM — top-level copy of the Bluetooth rune above.
